    "io.github.oaslananka/kicad-mcp-pro": {
      "longDescription": "KiCad MCP Pro is a production-grade MCP server for KiCad EDA. It provides 225+ tools for PCB design, schematic capture, DRC/ERC validation, BOM generation, simulation, DFM analysis, and manufacturing export. Integrates with Claude Code, ChatGPT, VS Code Copilot, Cursor, and other MCP hosts. Uses KiCad CLI for file-backed operations when KiCad is available on PATH.",
